{"tha-ap411:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap411:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap411:0.3":"Jatukannittheraapadana ","tha-ap411:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap411:1.2":"setthiputto ahosaham; ","tha-ap411:1.3":"Samappito kamagune, ","tha-ap411:1.4":"paricaremaham tada. ","tha-ap411:2.1":"Tato pasadamaruyha, ","tha-ap411:2.2":"mahabhoge valanjako; ","tha-ap411:2.3":"Tattha naccehi gitehi, ","tha-ap411:2.4":"paricaremaham tada. ","tha-ap411:3.1":"Turiya ahata mayham, ","tha-ap411:3.2":"sammatalasamahita; ","tha-ap411:3.3":"Naccanta itthiyo sabba, ","tha-ap411:3.4":"harantiyeva me mano. ","tha-ap411:4.1":"Celapika vamanika, ","tha-ap411:4.2":"kunjavasi timajjhika; ","tha-ap411:4.3":"Langhika sokajjhayi ca, ","tha-ap411:4.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap411:5.1":"Vetalino kumbhathuni, ","tha-ap411:5.2":"nata ca naccaka bahu; ","tha-ap411:5.3":"Nataka nataka ceva, ","tha-ap411:5.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap411:6.1":"Kappaka nhapaka suda, ","tha-ap411:6.2":"malakara supasaka; ","tha-ap411:6.3":"Jalla malla ca te sabbe, ","tha-ap411:6.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap411:7.1":"Etesu kilamanesu, ","tha-ap411:7.2":"sikkhite katupasane; ","tha-ap411:7.3":"Rattindivam na janami, ","tha-ap411:7.4":"indova tidasangane. ","tha-ap411:8.1":"Addhika pathika sabbe, ","tha-ap411:8.2":"yacaka varaka bahu; ","tha-ap411:8.3":"Upagacchanti te niccam, ","tha-ap411:8.4":"bhikkhayanta mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:9.1":"Samana brahmana ceva, ","tha-ap411:9.2":"punnakkhetta anuttara; ","tha-ap411:9.3":"Vaddhayanta mamam punnam, ","tha-ap411:9.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:10.1":"Pataga latuka sabbe, ","tha-ap411:10.2":"nigantha pupphasataka; ","tha-ap411:10.3":"Tedandika ekasikha, ","tha-ap411:10.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:11.1":"Ajivaka viluttavi, ","tha-ap411:11.2":"godhamma devadhammika; ","tha-ap411:11.3":"Rajojalladhara ete, ","tha-ap411:11.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:12.1":"Parittaka santipatta, ","tha-ap411:12.2":"kodhapugganika bahu; ","tha-ap411:12.3":"Tapassi vanacari ca, ","tha-ap411:12.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:13.1":"Oddaka damila ceva, ","tha-ap411:13.2":"sakula malavalaka; ","tha-ap411:13.3":"Savara yonaka ceva, ","tha-ap411:13.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:14.1":"Andhaka mundaka sabbe, ","tha-ap411:14.2":"kotala hanuvindaka; ","tha-ap411:14.3":"Aravacinarattha ca, ","tha-ap411:14.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:15.1":"Alasandaka pallavaka, ","tha-ap411:15.2":"dhammara niggamanusa; ","tha-ap411:15.3":"Gehika cetaputta ca, ","tha-ap411:15.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:16.1":"Madhuraka kosalaka, ","tha-ap411:16.2":"kalinga hatthiporika; ","tha-ap411:16.3":"Isinda makkala ceva, ","tha-ap411:16.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:17.1":"Celavaka arabbha ca, ","tha-ap411:17.2":"oghulha meghala bahu; ","tha-ap411:17.3":"Khuddaka suddaka ceva, ","tha-ap411:17.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:18.1":"Rohana sindhava ceva, ","tha-ap411:18.2":"citaka ekakannika; ","tha-ap411:18.3":"Surattha aparanta ca, ","tha-ap411:18.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:19.1":"Supparaka kumara ca, ","tha-ap411:19.2":"mallasovannabhumika; ","tha-ap411:19.3":"Vajjitanga ca te sabbe, ","tha-ap411:19.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:20.1":"Nalakara pesakara, ","tha-ap411:20.2":"cammakara ca tacchaka; ","tha-ap411:20.3":"Kammara kumbhakara ca, ","tha-ap411:20.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:21.1":"Manikara lohakara, ","tha-ap411:21.2":"sonnakara ca dussika; ","tha-ap411:21.3":"Tipukara ca te sabbe, ","tha-ap411:21.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:22.1":"Usukara bhamakara, ","tha-ap411:22.2":"pesakara ca gandhika; ","tha-ap411:22.3":"Rajaka tunnavaya ca, ","tha-ap411:22.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:23.1":"Telika katthahara ca, ","tha-ap411:23.2":"udahara ca pessika; ","tha-ap411:23.3":"Supika suparakkha ca, ","tha-ap411:23.4":"agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:24.1":"Dovarika anikattha, ","tha-ap411:24.2":"Bandhika pupphachaddaka; ","tha-ap411:24.3":"Hattharuha hatthipala, ","tha-ap411:24.4":"Agacchanti mamam gharam. ","tha-ap411:25.1":"Anandassa maharanno, ","tha-ap411:25.2":"mamatthassa adasaham; ","tha-ap411:25.3":"Sattavannena ratanena, ","tha-ap411:25.4":"unattham purayamaham. ","tha-ap411:26.1":"Ye maya kittita sabbe, ","tha-ap411:26.2":"nanavanna bahu jana; ","tha-ap411:26.3":"Tesaham cittamannaya, ","tha-ap411:26.4":"tappayim ratanenaham. ","tha-ap411:27.1":"Vaggusu bhasamanasu, ","tha-ap411:27.2":"vajjamanasu bherisu; ","tha-ap411:27.3":"Sankhesu dhamayantesu, ","tha-ap411:27.4":"sakagehe ramamaham. ","tha-ap411:28.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap411:28.2":"padumuttaranayako; ","tha-ap411:28.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap411:28.4":"parikkhinasavehi so. ","tha-ap411:29.1":"Bhikkhuhi sahito vithim, ","tha-ap411:29.2":"patipajjittha cakkhuma; ","tha-ap411:29.3":"Obhasento disa sabba, ","tha-ap411:29.4":"diparukkhova jotati. ","tha-ap411:30.1":"Vajjanti bheriyo sabba, ","tha-ap411:30.2":"gacchante lokanayake; ","tha-ap411:30.3":"Pabha niddhavate tassa, ","tha-ap411:30.4":"sataramsiva uggato. ","tha-ap411:31.1":"Kavatantarikayapi, ","tha-ap411:31.2":"pavitthena ca rasmina; ","tha-ap411:31.3":"Antogharesu vipulo, ","tha-ap411:31.4":"aloko asi tavade. ","tha-ap411:32.1":"Pabham disvana buddhassa, ","tha-ap411:32.2":"parisajje avocaham; ","tha-ap411:32.3":"‘Nissamsayam buddhasettho, ","tha-ap411:32.4":"imam vithimupagato’. ","tha-ap411:33.1":"Khippam oruyha pasada, ","tha-ap411:33.2":"agamim antarapanam; ","tha-ap411:33.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap411:33.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap411:34.1":"‘Anukampatu me buddho, ","tha-ap411:34.2":"jalajuttamanayako; ","tha-ap411:34.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap411:34.4":"adhivasesi so muni’. ","tha-ap411:35.1":"Nimantetvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap411:35.2":"abhinesim sakam gharam; ","tha-ap411:35.3":"Tattha annena panena, ","tha-ap411:35.4":"santappesim mahamunim. ","tha-ap411:36.1":"Bhuttavim kalamannaya, ","tha-ap411:36.2":"buddhasetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap411:36.3":"Satangikena turiyena, ","tha-ap411:36.4":"buddhasettham upatthahim. ","tha-ap411:37.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap411:37.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap411:37.3":"Antoghare nisiditva, ","tha-ap411:37.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap411:38.1":"‘Yo mam turiyehupatthasi, ","tha-ap411:38.2":"annapanancadasi me; ","tha-ap411:38.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap411:38.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap411:39.1":"Pahutabhakkho hutvana, ","tha-ap411:39.2":"sahiranno sabhojano; ","tha-ap411:39.3":"Catudipe ekarajjam, ","tha-ap411:39.4":"karayissatiyam naro. ","tha-ap411:40.1":"Panca sile samadaya, ","tha-ap411:40.2":"dasakammapathe tato; ","tha-ap411:40.3":"Samadaya pavattento, ","tha-ap411:40.4":"parisam sikkhapayissati. ","tha-ap411:41.1":"Turiyasatasahassani, ","tha-ap411:41.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap411:41.3":"Vajjayissantimam niccam, ","tha-ap411:41.4":"upatthanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap411:42.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap411:42.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap411:42.3":"Catusatthikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap411:42.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap411:43.1":"Catusatthikkhattum raja, ","tha-ap411:43.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap411:43.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap411:43.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap411:44.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap411:44.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap411:44.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap411:44.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap411:45.1":"Upapajjati yam yonim, ","tha-ap411:45.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap411:45.3":"Anunabhogo hutvana, ","tha-ap411:45.4":"manussattam gamissati. ","tha-ap411:46.1":"Ajjhayako bhavitvana, ","tha-ap411:46.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap411:46.3":"Uttamattham gavesanto, ","tha-ap411:46.4":"carissati mahim imam. ","tha-ap411:47.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap411:47.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap411:47.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap411:47.4":"sasanebhiramissati. ","tha-ap411:48.1":"Aradhayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap411:48.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap411:48.3":"Kilese jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap411:48.4":"arahayam bhavissati’. ","tha-ap411:49.1":"Vipine byaggharajava, ","tha-ap411:49.2":"migarajava kesari; ","tha-ap411:49.3":"Abhito viharamajja, ","tha-ap411:49.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap411:50.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap411:50.2":"dalidde duggatimhi va; ","tha-ap411:50.3":"Nibbattim me na passami, ","tha-ap411:50.4":"upatthanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap411:51.1":"Vivekamanuyuttomhi, ","tha-ap411:51.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap411:51.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap411:51.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap411:52.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap411:52.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap411:52.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap411:53.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap411:53.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap411:53.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap411:54.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap411:54.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap411:54.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap411:55.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma jatukannitthero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap411:56.1":"Jatukannittherassapadanam navamam. "}